@startuml
title Browser Auth Bundle Boundary (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "Browser User" as User #DCEBFA
component "Client Component\n(header/login/reset-password)" as Client #FDE2E2
component "lib/auth/athena-browser-auth.ts" as BrowserAuth #FDE2E2
component "utils/athena/auth-client.ts" as SharedAuthFactory #FDE2E2
component "@xylex-group/athena dist/index.js" as AthenaSdk #FDE2E2
component "Node-only deps\npg, fs/promises, net, tls, util/types" as NodeDeps #FCA5A5
component "Next.js client bundler" as Bundler #FDE68A

User --> Client : interacts with auth UI
Client --> BrowserAuth : import + call auth methods
BrowserAuth --> SharedAuthFactory : imports createAthenaAuthClient()
SharedAuthFactory --> AthenaSdk : imports createClient()
AthenaSdk --> NodeDeps : static runtime imports
Bundler --> NodeDeps : tries to resolve for browser

note right of Bundler
Client build fails with
\"Can't resolve fs/promises/net/tls\"
because server runtime code
crosses into client graph.
end note
@enduml
